{"tid":2008694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高雄有市民以高壓水槍宣傳6.6 罷韓","createTime":"2020-05-09T08:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T09:44:56.000Z","uid":3747,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"912629c96f91dfc86a0534f8e6ae665974eec0e2","tid":2008694,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:22:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/348571125292077/posts/1666745066808003/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F348571125292077%2Fposts%2F1666745066808003%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7dw1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=5c719b4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/348571125292077/posts/1666745066808003/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n#強力洗潔地面 #罷韓創意無限<br />\n　<br />\n今天晚上，台灣基進高雄黨部新聞部主任黃柏翔帶領志工們來到 #四維行政中心 替高雄清潔人行道，不只 #百大路口 還要 #萬巷更新 ！<br />\n　<br />\n自從罷免三階開始，韓國瑜就不斷透過各種手段，選擇性執法，來拆除罷免看板，為了突破困境，繼續向高雄市民宣傳罷免，提醒大家 #因為愛高雄 #做伙出來投<br />\n　<br />\n台灣基進改良網友建議，以 #清潔地板，做 #罷免看板 ，以完全合法的方式，替高雄大掃除，<br />\n期待六月六號之後，高雄可以 #萬象更新 ！<br />\n　<br />\n#清潔地板 #不是潑漆 #請勿抹黑<br />\n#一起用創意愛高雄<br />\n　<br />\n#因為愛高雄 #做伙出來投<br />\n#六月六號星期六 #投票罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hgi2cB0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHgi2cB0.jpg&h=de5ae2d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06ac12d8e0f4a8d8e0586d0e6cbb070bf63e1471","tid":2008694,"uid":107681,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T08:55:06.000Z","msg":"洗地e招幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食環將來要負責整污漕返個地下"},{"pid":"c97b85bcfd044a98cd5b09ff1aa5aa208df6c439","tid":2008694,"uid":55089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/h